snippet: LANDIS--Elayne S. Jewish Board of Family and Children's Services mourns the passing of Elayne S. Landis, who was a steadfast and generous supporter of JBFCS' Child Development Center. Our hearts and thoughts are with Elayne's family....
lead_paragraph: LANDIS--Elayne S. Jewish Board of Family and Children's Services mourns the passing of Elayne S. Landis, who was a steadfast and generous supporter of JBFCS' Child Development Center. Our hearts and thoughts are with Elayne's family.
